				<td colspan="2"><span>Well I have been skimming over the bard creation guides and it seems to me like a Human may be, good to the fact that they dont have the low DEX of the cat and the good stamina
<br />

<br />
What REALLY is the best stats for a bard?
<br />

<br />
I mean STA will make sure you dont get owned due to hit points, but we need DEX and CHA to pull off songs and charms and mezzes.
<br />

<br />
Has anyone actually made a Human bard? heh.
<br />

<br />
I hardly ever see any on Povar
<br />

<br />
I looked at the creation guide on Casters Realm but I am not sure i agree with the points division they list</span></td>
