				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Any human bards?<a name="23358"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 23 04 10:12 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>LOTS of Human Bards out there.  Especially Rallos Zek and Veeshan worshippers because of the sweet Heraldic Armors available.
<br />

<br />
Check in the Guides section.  Steppy's guide, &quot;Getting Started With Your Bard&quot; is excellent.
<br />

<br />
The differences in starting stats among races is completely trivial at higher levels, because you can boost any of your stats easily with gear.
<br />

<br />
Some say that CHA is hardest to max at high levels, others go with STA all the way.
<br />

<br />
The biggest pain with Humans in night blindness.  If you are making a twink, get him an ultravision item, and no problem.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
