				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Any human bards?<a name="23828"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 25 04 12:15 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>One of my bards is human.
<br />

<br />
Just keep your eyes open for night blindness enhancing items (Foreman's skull cap for instance, black alloy items). The rest is pretty much the same.
<br />

<br />
Getting track/forage/safefall later than some other classes is a minor inconvenience.
<br />

<br />
I went a big boost into stamina, since I tank this boy a little more than my main bard, it helps.  There is not much else to say, other than there are droppable items in the game (Grieves of the Orcish Master/Architects BP...etc) that make the diety based armors less of a factor for me.
<br />

<br />
Good luck!</span></td>
